strings.Value: "Why does no one go hunting? If someone is expecting me to do it, they'll be sorely disappointed!"
"I wouldn't say no to a bowl of tasty stew. It's a shame no one is going to hunt."
"I've more important thing to do than crawl through the brush in search of rabbits and deer!"
"We could set a snare. Though I doubt we could ever actually catch anything here."
"I don't like it when you behave like this. We're your friends, not your servants or slaves."
"Affirmative! I'll get right on it, Your Excellency..."
"Not me! That last time when I brought that fat tasty toad, you all made mean faces... Nok-Nok never good hunter!"
"Agreed! Can't any of you find food? It must be plentiful in such fertile lands!"
"Agreed! Can't any of you find food? It must be plentiful in such fertile lands!"
